.SH "NAME"
org.freedesktop.timesync1 \- The D\-Bus interface of systemd\-timesyncd
.SH "INTRODUCTION"
.PP
\fBsystemd-timesyncd.service\fR(8)
is a system service that may be used to synchronize the local system clock with a remote Network Time Protocol (NTP) server\&. This page describes the D\-Bus interface\&.
